Chaos Caught on Camera premieres on the Science Channel on Monday, April 13 . 
  The series reveals the extraordinary footage taken by people in the middle of a disaster . 
  It gives a unique perspective of real life or death situations . 
  One skydiver was caught in a deadly collision after a plane crashed into him . 
  An Illinois man had his camera on hand as a deadly tornado tore through his town . 
  Each incident is deconstructed with graphics and illustrations . 
 